SUMMARY:TRACES IN TIME
LOCATION:Bridgeport Art Center\, 1200 W 35th St\, Chicago\, IL 60609
DESCRIPTION:Curated by Kelvin Larue Taylor 3RD FLOOR GALLERY This exhibit
 ion focuses on works that explore memory\, the marks we leave behind\, a
 nd the passage of time. Each piece creates a dialogue between permanence
  and transience\, asking: What do we leave behind\, and what do we carry
  forward?...\nMore info: https://thevisualist.org/2026/01/traces-in-time
 /\nVenue site: https://www.bridgeportart.com/traces-in-time/
